At the client`s house, Khloe pushes Kenna onto the bed stating that if they`re going to wash these sheets they may as well use them first. She certainly won`t take no for an answer. As she disciplines her, she tells her that since she seems to have made herself at home, she may as well continue.
title: Will Work For Pussy
